{"tid":846520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府精神科係咪醫院最佳扮工部門？","createTime":"2018-10-03T13:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T00:42:08.000Z","uid":37525,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d986f1e7b42754e8c7e4de279ddc4354b3c3c0f","tid":846520,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"- 門診精神科醫生<br />\n排隊登記輪候 2-3個鐘<br />\n入醫生房 傾3分鐘<br />\n開藥 約期 走得<br />\n(主要係開藥，覆診係攞藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n- 心理學家<br />\n排期9個月至兩年<br />\n(又係)登記輪候坐2個鐘<br />\n入房傾10-15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n病人話無病徵/聲稱有改善<br />\n就照樣鳩寫、hea睇<br />\n完全片面之詞，無實質治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見多4-5次，乜撚都無做過<br />\n就話病人已經無乜事<br />\n可研究唔使再嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁排期睇嚟做乜？<br />\n乜撚幫助都無<br />\n只係每日有幾粒藥丸<br />\n當糖仔/安慰劑食吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ef3e6af1863458cd2a3478981e127d2f22adc8","tid":846520,"uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"你成日去睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c782ff70fe49b555309794a18aab7dccbd71a0c0","tid":846520,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecacf6d2cb472a79b42a6517c1a7ee98e8f27ee","tid":846520,"uid":37525,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"仲有精神科社康護士<br />\n<br />\n叫個男護士<br />\n上女病人屋企探訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每月上嚟寒暄幾句同數藥丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n透過算術嚟評估病人食藥情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟多幾次見無乜嘢/搬咗第二區<br />\n就唔再follow<br />\n<br />\n(其實像徵式探訪<br />\n作用/意義都不大<br />\n但醫生又會話: <br />\n已經轉介咗好多服務同支援畀你哋<br />\n幾方面都做緊嘢嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3a1a2d77d05b922e9c89923414369f9d02e0a5","tid":846520,"uid":37525,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"55ef3e6af1863458cd2a3478981e127d2f22adc8","tid":846520,"uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"你成日去睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"我成日諗<br />\n如果屋企某人<br />\n交通意外身故<br />\n咁大家都係解脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔使而家咁<br />\n浪費時間 毫無進展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但醫生又會話: 已經食住藥<br />\n控制緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實 食同唔食<br />\n無撚分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f54f090f70a0e6e2d2e71aebb9fe54465fda80e","tid":846520,"uid":126100,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"因為心理病難measure好多，醫生話你好就好，差就差，要交功課做&ldquo;業績&rdquo;好易刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ef9c12031aa1a5399fa7eeb877c6c9854bab62","tid":846520,"uid":15659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"有冇攞傷殘津貼先？"},{"pid":"10669449f606f9a64cb501c2a19ab018a974baa4","tid":846520,"uid":37525,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f54f090f70a0e6e2d2e71aebb9fe54465fda80e","tid":846520,"uid":126100,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"因為心理病難measure好多，醫生話你好就好，差就差，要交功課做&ldquo;業績&rdquo;好易刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"乜呢啲都要跑數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畀啲良心啦 好心<br />\n病人排咗咁撚耐先輪得到<br />\n每次登記完又喺出面等成幾個鐘<br />\n未計車程來回<br />\n<br />\n花費大半日時間嚟睇醫生<br />\n但只係得到流水式面診<br />\nHea鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c273a92b04034fd5d6ea65c40a71cf8ed1b842d","tid":846520,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"99ef9c12031aa1a5399fa7eeb877c6c9854bab62","tid":846520,"uid":15659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"有冇攞傷殘津貼先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"咁係咪平衡返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無心醫 醫唔好<br />\n即係成世攞津貼/綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交埋嘅稅 有部分就係養呢啲人<br />\n人數不斷增加 而且係養一世"},{"pid":"f243e519f9d4806daebace4e6b352285232f47f0","tid":846520,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"收皮啦公立醫院，只係識開藥同開藥"},{"pid":"5405c0b9a24d826bd54eff8015b83378f9161c97","tid":846520,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"一分錢一分貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bb88abd44a90986b174c46bf3373c40ba8f5b9","tid":846520,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f243e519f9d4806daebace4e6b352285232f47f0","tid":846520,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"收皮啦公立醫院，只係識開藥同開藥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"私家醫生係好好多"},{"pid":"2e3b4428d9f6e63535b095a12ec1e9abc1e8df1a","tid":846520,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":